---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/about-cover.jpeg";
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Software Developer, Kubestronaut, and Cloud Native Specialist."
	pubDate={new Date("July 05 2026")}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hey there, I'm Abhigyan! I'm a Software Engineer and CNCF Kubestronaut
		building scalable and intelligent AI-native systems. I love geeking out
		over Tech, AI/ML, and everything Cloud Native.
	</p>

	<p>
		Previously, I was a FullStack Developer at ArthurSpaces. My go-to tech
		stack usually involves Go, TypeScript, Python, and React Native, running
		on top of Kubernetes and Argo. I'm also a huge believer in learning in
		public, so this blog is my little corner of the internet to share my
		technical deep dives, experiments, and thoughts on modern
		infrastructure.
	</p>

	<p>
		When I'm not deploying workloads or tinkering with new system
		architectures, you can usually find me unwinding with old American and
		European classic movies, or occasionally catching up on some anime.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm always down to chat about tech, brainstorm ideas, or discuss
		opportunities. Say hi on <a
			href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abhigyan-mohanta/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a
		>, follow my ramblings on <a
			href="https://x.com/MohantaAbhigyan"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a
		>, or check out my repos on <a
			href="https://github.com/ABHIGYAN-MOHANTA"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a
		>!
	</p>
</Layout>
